ComicInfo.Summary:
Ringing Up Baby: A man Cadence met at the club the previous evening calls her up for a date, but gets cold feet while waiting for her to pick up.
The Perils Of Celina: The Pink Soft Cream girls engage in a little role-playing based on the cliche of the nineteenth century blackmail morality play.
Rough Housing: A pair of foxes engage in a little rough role-playing
Chain Reaction: A cat girl role plays with her bull boy-toy.
